column16: Mitch Moreland flies out to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.
Xander Bogaerts flies out to right fielder Aaron Judge.
Dustin Pedroia grounds out, second baseman Ronald Torreyes to first baseman Austin Romine.
Mookie Betts strikes out swinging, catcher Gary Sanchez to first baseman Austin Romine.
Eric Young Jr.   singles on a line drive to shortstop Didi Gregorius, deflected by pitcher Ben Heller.   Andrelton Simmons scores.    Cliff Pennington to 2nd.
Martin Maldonado grounds out softly, pitcher Ben Heller to first baseman Chris Carter.   Andrelton Simmons to 3rd.
